Static Property# ColorSchemes

A static property that allows you to access to access the look color scheme enumeration.MapKit JS 5.13+

```
static ColorSchemes: typeof ColorScheme;
```

## [Discussion](/documentation/MapKitJS/Map/ColorSchemes#Discussion)

Use this object to access the [`ColorScheme`](/documentation/mapkitjs/colorscheme) enumeration with `mapkit.Map.ColorSchemes`.
